data.description: Solid Brick Ranch in great Frog Pond Rd. location. Home built by owner who is a long-time area contractor, now retired. Recent update to kitchen with new solid surface countertops. All new replacement windows and new storm doors. Cozy family room with fireplace and woodburner insert. Excellent garden spot. Owners retiring to N.C. to enjoy Grandkids. Please bring showings to help this dream come true! PRICED $15,000 UNDER ASSESSMENT.
